CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 19, reads: "4. Sales representative Lee Fannell and Miss Willa Rogers served delicious O & H wieners from the Oswald & Hess Company booth.."
TitMainTitle: Lee Fannell and Willa Rogers standing in Oswald & Hess Packing Company booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
